answers.answer: It is  common during pregnancy to have trace amounts of protein in ur wee
Its called preeclampsia.    You can look it up for more details or ask ur dr.  I had it with my 2nd born.
I'm so sorry you went through that! How much water have you been drinking lately? Maybe you need more water that can help lower the protien. Not having high blood pressure is a good sign:) Good luck!
